<h2 id="사용법">사용법</h2>

<blockquote>
  <p>REF</p>

  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://wikieducator.org/Help:LaTeX_Symbol_Tables_-_Mathematics">Help:LaTeX Symbol Tables - Mathematics</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://www.codecogs.com/latex/eqneditor.php">수식 입력기</a></li>
  </ul>
</blockquote>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>inline<br />
$\chi^2$분포 확률변수 $\sum_{i=1}^{n}\chi_i^2$의 분포</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>기본<br />
<script type="math/tex">\sum\_{i=1}^{n}\chi\_i^2</script><br />
<script type="math/tex">\because s\_d = \sqrt{\frac{\sum (d - \bar{d})^2}{n -1}} = \sqrt{\frac{\sum (y - \bar{y})^2}{n -1}} = s\_y</script></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>줄바꿈 : <code class="highlighter-rouge">\\</code> &lt; 2개 입력해야 작동함<br />
<script type="math/tex">s\_d = s\_y \\
\because s\_d = \sqrt{\frac{\sum (d - \bar{d})^2}{n -1}} = \sqrt{\frac{\sum (y - \bar{y})^2}{n -1}} = s\_y</script></p>

    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>$$
s_d = s_y \\
\because s_d = \sqrt{\frac{\sum (d - \bar{d})^2}{n -1}} = \sqrt{\frac{\sum (y - \bar{y})^2}{n -1}} = s_y
$$
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ul>

